data.description: Check out this lovely 2.5 story home located on 5 acres with a mother-in-law suite and a huge barn that has lots to offer. No city taxes. Main house HVAC installed 2019, HVAC mother-in-law suite installed 2021, and Roof replaced 2019, new carpet 2nd floor, new LVP flooring throughout all downstairs, fully remodeled kitchens, and seller is leaving all appliances including washers and dryers. There is a trench dug on the left side and backside of the property estimated 5ft deep.The home has multiple rooms with endless space.  Home is Sold-As-Is. Some of the vinyl siding is missing. Seller will be completing the mother in law side of siding only. This is a must see, schedule a private tour today with listing agent Brandy Collins (910)852-1474.
